<subSubSection id="72A1650E0A130924379BF894C20CF823" pageId="3" pageNumber="425" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph id="3A0436850A130924379BF894C20CF823" blockId="3.[151,1437,1892,2027]" pageId="3" pageNumber="425">
<emphasis id="08CFEA970A130924379BF894C74AF8B6" bold="true" box="[151,274,1892,1918]" pageId="3" pageNumber="425">Diagnosis.</emphasis>
This species was described from 
<collectingRegion id="F87FF8670A1309243583F894C4AAF8B6" box="[655,754,1892,1918]" country="China" name="Guizhou" pageId="3" pageNumber="425">Guizhou</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="42AC76150A13092435F2F894C51CF8B6" box="[766,836,1892,1918]" name="China" pageId="3" pageNumber="425">China</collectingCountry>
, and the illustrations of male genitalia were provided by 
<bibRefCitation id="5E2A4B740A13092437B6F878C73BF86B" author="Li, Z. Z. &amp; Dai, R. H. &amp; Xing, J. C." box="[186,355,1928,1955]" pageId="3" pageNumber="425" refId="ref4322" refString="Li, Z. Z., Dai, R. H. &amp; Xing, J. C. (2011) Deltocephalinae from China (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae). Popular Science Press, Beijing, 336 pp. [in Chinese with English summary]" type="book" year="2011">
Li 
<emphasis id="08CFEA970A13092437D5F879C751F86A" box="[217,265,1928,1954]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="425">et al</emphasis>
. (2011)
</bibRefCitation>
. This species has an inner process extending from the base of the pygofer to posterior margin and curved ventrally and the gonopore at the apex of the aedeagal process. These characters indicate that this species should be excluded from 
<taxonomicName id="FDBB4D060A13092436B8F820C43CF822" authorityName="Ishihara" authorityYear="1961" box="[436,612,2000,2026]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Phlogothamnus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="425" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="08CFEA970A13092436B8F820C43CF822" box="[436,612,2000,2026]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="425">Phlogothamnus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and tranferred to 
<taxonomicName id="FDBB4D060A1309243420F820C208F823" authority="Ribaut, 1942" authorityName="Ribaut" authorityYear="1942" box="[812,1104,2000,2027]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Phlogotettix" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="425" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="08CFEA970A1309243420F820C5EDF822" box="[812,949,2000,2026]" italics="true" pageId="3" pageNumber="425">Phlogotettix</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="5E2A4B740A13092434B0F820C208F823" author="Ribaut, H." box="[956,1104,2000,2027]" pageId="3" pageNumber="425" pagination="259 - 270" refId="ref4512" refString="Ribaut, H. (1942) Demembrement des generes Athysanus Burm. et Thamnottetix Zett. [Homoptera-Jassidae]. Bulletin de la Societe d'Histoire Naturelle de Toulouse, 77, 259 - 270." type="journal article" year="1942">Ribaut, 1942</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
